Ursa

Claws bared and fur bristling, Ursa, the ferocious Dota champion, dominates this digital fan art. The dynamic illustration captures Ursa's primal power, their imposing form a testament to their savage strength.

Kayod Lang

An inspiring yet heartwrenching portrayal of the everyday man in the Philippines just trying his best at life. The true essence of the phrase - "Kayod lang", and the epitome of hope amidst trials.

Seed

A seed can mean many things; the start of a new life, the promise of something new, and a chance for growth. This illustration is meant to portray the different possibilities life can take us.

Girl With The Star
